    "body": "<h3>Bug Fixes</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>checkbox:</strong> align checkbox properly in item using start alignment (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/29850\">#29850</a>) (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/commit/88b701363c1865e81d7d136acab4b9fef3b1ab7a\">88b7013</a>), closes <a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/29837\">#29837</a></li>\n<li><strong>datetime:</strong> display today's date and time when value is an empty string (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/29839\">#29839</a>) (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/commit/f1d50c0f645b3adf51426c24a1da0bbd1223f1d5\">f1d50c0</a>), closes <a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/29669\">#29669</a></li>\n<li><strong>range:</strong> disable scroll when range is being dragged (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/29241\">#29241</a>) (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/commit/35b1a459294657b609f683457e71babd4673a3a8\">35b1a45</a>)</li>\n<li><strong>react, vue:</strong> add default value for navManager on tabs (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/29865\">#29865</a>) (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/commit/df39ceac6db6511518aed4766e6a59aa24fb53ec\">df39cea</a>)</li>\n<li><strong>react:</strong> revert react output target version (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/29869\">#29869</a>) (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/commit/f64458dc63a05acb955aa1f2ec3755c738466cf4\">f64458d</a>), closes <a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/stencil-ds-output-targets/issues/476\">ionic-team/stencil-ds-output-targets#476</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/stencil-ds-output-targets/issues/475\">ionic-team/stencil-ds-output-targets#475</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/29848\">#29848</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
