    "body": "<h3>Features</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>checkbox:</strong> display as block when justify or alignment properties are defined (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/29783\">#29783</a>) (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/commit/4ccd15e47ad4ec7cb59d2694c5738eab1bb265ff\">4ccd15e</a>)</li>\n<li><strong>radio:</strong> display as block when justify or alignment properties are defined (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/29801\">#29801</a>) (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/commit/18b02b3574f54a2f377f5bfe4e074bf015418dd3\">18b02b3</a>)</li>\n<li><strong>react, vue, angular:</strong> use tabs without router (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/29794\">#29794</a>) (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/commit/867066b4eba369de025f3c7c8ef33e7089cdf3bc\">867066b</a>), closes <a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/25184\">#25184</a></li>\n<li><strong>toggle:</strong> display as block when justify or alignment properties are defined (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/29802\">#29802</a>) (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/commit/0332c8c6ceb612840e73f789d5c5b66f05cb53d4\">0332c8c</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n",
